snippet.title: Wipeout 2600 - Atari 2600 Homebrew
snippet.description:
Ever wondered what would the classic futuristic racer look like if it came out on the Atari 2600? Wonder no more, as Retro Lord created this homebrew demake of wipEout way back in 2015.

Steer with the joystick, avoid the other racers, or shoot them with your missiles. Speed up with the speed boosts and refill the clock with the energy points.

wipEout (C) Sony Interactive Entertainment
Developed with batari Basic
Download: https://forums.atariage.com/topic/234985-wipeout-2600/
